\"main\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\u003carticle id=\"post-22404\"\u003e\n\n\t\n\t\n\u003cdiv data-ast-blocks-layout=\"true\"\u003e\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis post may contain affiliate links. Read my \u003ca href=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/legal/\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"follow\"\u003edisclosure policy\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis homemade Blue Cheese Dressing recipe made with Greek yogurt is creamy, tangy, and packed with real blue cheese flavor—no buttermilk required!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1800\" fetchpriority=\"high\" data-pin-description=\"This Greek Yogurt Blue Cheese Dressing is thick, tangy, and easy—no buttermilk needed. Perfect for wedge salads, wings, or dipping. #dressing\" data-pin-title=\"Greek Yogurt Blue Cheese Dressing Recipe (No Buttermilk)\" src=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-8.jpg\" alt=\"Blue Cheese Dressing Recipe\" srcset=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-8.jpg 1200w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-8-500x750.jpg 500w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-8-550x825.jpg 550w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-8-170x255.jpg 170w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-8-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-8-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-8-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-8-600x900.jpg 600w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-8-260x390.jpg 260w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-8-150x225.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you’ve ever bought buttermilk just for one recipe, only to toss the rest—this blue cheese dressing is for you. Made with protein-rich Greek yogurt and no buttermilk, it’s thick, creamy, and loaded with tangy blue cheese. Perfect for drizzling over \u003ca href=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/chopped-wedge-salad/\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"follow\"\u003ewedge salads\u003c/a\u003e, dunking \u003ca href=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/lighter-buffalo-wings-6-pts/\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"follow\"\u003ebuffalo wings\u003c/a\u003e, or spooning onto a steak sandwich. It’s an easy, better-for-you twist on the classic that skips the extra fuss (and waste). Most readers commented this tastes even better the next day and thickens up in the fridge making this perfect for make-ahead prep.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"callout-box-block_4928aa160b8186a8088cbfa9e35b45d7\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e Why This Works\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eI tested this blue cheese dressing many years ago while developing a lighter spin for a classic steakhouse-style wedge salad and ended up loving it as a dip, too.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"237\" data-end=\"286\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"239\" data-end=\"286\"\u003eNo buttermilk needed—so nothing goes to waste\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"287\" data-end=\"347\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"289\" data-end=\"347\"\u003eMade with Greek yogurt for a lighter, high-protein twist\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"348\" data-end=\"398\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"350\" data-end=\"398\"\u003eJust a touch of mayo for classic creamy flavor\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"399\" data-end=\"439\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"401\" data-end=\"439\"\u003eReady in minutes—no blender required\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"440\" data-end=\"489\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"442\" data-end=\"489\"\u003ePerfect for salads, wings, or dipping veggies\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-start=\"440\" data-end=\"489\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"442\" data-end=\"489\"\u003eHealthier Than Store Bought – No weird ingredients, and it’s also more economical\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor more of my favorite salad dressing recipes, try my \u003ca href=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/low-fat-buttermilk-ranch-dressing/\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"follow\"\u003eButtermilk Ranch Dressing\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/skinny-caesar-dressing/\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"follow\"\u003eGreek Yogurt Caesar Dressing\u003c/a\u003e, and \u003ca href=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/basil-green-goddess-dressing/\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"follow\"\u003eGreek Goddess Salad Dressing.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003eIngredients You’ll Need\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eI prefer preparing homemade blue cheese salad dressing over buying it because I know exactly what’s in it and can use clean ingredients. Here’s what you’ll need \u003cstrong\u003e(see recipe card for exact measurements)\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1800\" data-pin-description=\"This Greek Yogurt Blue Cheese Dressing is thick, tangy, and easy—no buttermilk needed. Perfect for wedge salads, wings, or dipping. #dressing\" data-pin-title=\"Greek Yogurt Blue Cheese Dressing Recipe (No Buttermilk)\" src=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-1.jpg\" alt=\"blue cheese, yogurt, mayo, lemon\" srcset=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-1.jpg 1200w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-1-500x750.jpg 500w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-1-550x825.jpg 550w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-1-170x255.jpg 170w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-1-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-1-600x900.jpg 600w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-1-260x390.jpg 260w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-1-150x225.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBlue Cheese:\u003c/strong\u003e Using high-quality blue cheese is essential for the best blue cheese dressing.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e0% Greek Yogurt \u003c/strong\u003emakes this dressing light but still creamy.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLight Mayonnaise\u003c/strong\u003e balances the tanginess of the Greek yogurt.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAcid:\u003c/strong\u003e Lemon juice and white wine vinegar thin the yogurt and complement the richness of the blue cheese.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSeasoning: \u003c/strong\u003eGarlic powder, salt, and black pepper enhance the overall taste.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003eHow to Make Blue Cheese Dressing\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eMaking homemade blue cheese dressing is as easy as 1-2-3! (\u003cstrong\u003eSee the printable instructions in the recipe card.\u003c/strong\u003e)\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" data-id=\"146301\" src=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-2-550x825.jpg\" alt=\"yogurt and blue cheese\" srcset=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-2-550x825.jpg 550w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-2-500x750.jpg 500w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-2-170x255.jpg 170w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-2-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-2-600x900.jpg 600w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-2-260x390.jpg 260w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-2-150x225.jpg 150w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Low-Fat-Creamy-Blue-Cheese-Dressing-2.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eMash the blue cheese and yogurt with a fork\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" data